eligibility_criteria.description:
Minimum age: 10 Years
Maximum age: 60 Years

No clinical or imaging evidence of distant metastases by PA and Lateral CXR,
             Radionuclide Bone scan, and LFTs including total bilirubin, ALT, AST, and alkaline
             phosphatase
In the presence of liver involvement, AST/ALT, alkaline phosphatase and total bilirubin must not exceed 3x ULN (i.e., must be < 3x ULN)
